{"tid":1374563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真post求推]聽晚唔止元朗有危險！！","createTime":"2019-07-27T19:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:01:38.000Z","uid":10973,"like":418,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"a99c0ea80cfe3a883d33a2fdc8947e8177fa2de6","tid":1374563,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:57:35.000Z","msg":"如果你地聽日會出遮打<br />\n而你地係住係危險地區（<span style=\"color: red;\">屯元天</span>/<span style=\"color: red;\">深水埗</span>/<span style=\"color: red;\">沙田</span>/<span style=\"color: red;\">旺角油麻地果欄</span>/<span style=\"color: orange;\">荃灣</span>/<span style=\"color: orange;\">尖沙嘴</span>/<span style=\"color: orange;\">大埔</span>/<span style=\"color: orange;\">上水粉嶺</span>）<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">排名有分次序</span><br />\n返屋企嘅途中<span style=\"color: red;\">務必小心</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 班老黑已經谷撚到就中風<br />\n眾所鳩知，香港法治係幾咁可信，黑警係幾咁可靠<br />\n仲等<span style=\"color: red;\">39分鐘</span>真係死撚得<br />\n<br />\n2.冇可能動員全香港入你個區出黎支援<br />\n議員/記者/手足都好大機會留係港島，<span style=\"color: red;\">分身乏術</span>，黑鐵都會唔停站<br />\n<br />\n3.有效維持<span style=\"color: red;\">群眾鬥群眾</span>嘅現象<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以記得換衫</span></span><br />\n你可能會覺得無差別攻擊，根本冇得避<br />\n但依個係<span style=\"color: red;\">signaling</span>嘅問題，白衫top target一定係黑衫後生仔女<br />\n唔好主動做target，20個白衫追一個黑衫 <br />\n其他手足係<span style=\"color: red;\">葉問都救你唔到</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有事 唔好驚</span></span><br />\n1.<span style=\"color: green;\">唔好落單 </span> 點都要痴埋一齊 大聲嗌到人人聽到<br />\n2.搵<span style=\"color: green;\">消防救護</span><br />\n3.人唔夠就<span style=\"color: green;\">忍住道氣 </span> 記住，傷一個，下次就少一個人上街<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">4.拍片係必須 但要自行判斷環境</span>全世界拍片係咪就可以救到俾人打到半死嘅手足/記者/市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">消防電話（只節錄部份高危地區）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新界</span></span><br />\n屯門消防局\t       電話: 2462 5717<br />\n天水圍消防局\t電話: 2448 0664<br />\n元朗消防局\t       電話: 2474 6732<br />\n八鄉消防局\t       電話: 2488 7282<br />\n沙田消防局\t       電話: 2691 0596<br />\n小瀝源消防局\t電話: 2647 7515<br />\n田心消防局\t       電話: 2694 8639<br />\n馬鞍山消防局\t電話: 2640 3222<br />\n大埔消防局\t       電話: 2651 2951<br />\n大埔東消防局\t電話: 2664 2511<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">九龍</span></span><br />\n旺角消防局\t       電話: 2396 6409<br />\n長沙灣消防局\t電話: 2729 5807<br />\n荔枝角消防局\t電話: 2742 4221<br />\n石硤尾消防局\t電話: 2778 1098<br />\n尖沙咀消防局\t電話: 2366 2389<br />\n紅磡消防局\t       電話: 2363 0207<br />\n尖東消防局\t       電話: 2722 4871<br />\n油麻地消防局\t電話: 2385 0307<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望以上資料用唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANFuVWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANFuVWm.png&h=0a02b421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGNHDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGNHDL.png&h=3666bc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dujznBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdujznBn.png&h=3e4a50b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22rU65r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22rU65r.png&h=2b18ebb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEjznDz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEjznDz.png&h=982d6aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"046a09d9d0f4544658515756d74540a5b56718a2","tid":1374563,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:58:36.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"3a006a543d9a366e0414f92434c1723741d